 angles of 25-28 degrees are considered. We provide suggested flare\nparameters to optimise future studies of this kind.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Mar 2013 20:51:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-03-27"}
