cal interpretation of the\nwavefunction is further developped. In particular, a physical interpretation\nfor the symmetry-quotienting maps is proposed, according to the Fourier\ndecomposition of the energy levels of the wavefunction of the universe, as far\nas the meaning of epochs and eras is concerned from a quantum point of view.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Mar 2013 23:02:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Apr 2013 18:35:38 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 16 Sep 2013 18:25:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-09-17"}
